! Xft 
! Thanks to https://old.reddit.com/r/i3wm/comments/driqb3/help_with_dpi_scaling/f6j808j/
Xft.hinting:    True
Xft.hintstyle:  hintfull
Xft.antialias:   1 
Xft.autohint:   False
Xft.lcdfilter:  lcddefault 
Xft.rgba:   rgb 
Xft.dpi:    120
